Hello Erica,
&nbsp;
We have an update for your query.
&nbsp;
Upon checking, we observed that the following products are not imported to the plugin.
&nbsp;
  Stuffed Pepper Soup - Case of 6  Tomato Basil Bisque - Case of 6  Tuscan Minestrone Soup - Case of 6  Potato &amp; Cheese Soup - Case of 6  Corn Chowder - Case of 6  Cock-a-doodle Noodle Soup - Case of 6  &nbsp;
The reason for this is we could see that you are using the "Product Visibility User Role for WooCommerce" plugin which restricts the visibility of the details to certain user roles, such as Wholesale. The above mentioned products have this restriction enabled (as shown in below screenshot).
Due to this, all the products associated with the order 5326 are not imported to the plugin.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
So, we request you to remove all the visibility restrictions to all the published products in your store. Once done, let us know, so we can try importing those products from our end.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
If you are not willing to remove this visibility restriction set for all the products, then you can remove this for certain products individually and we can then import those products to the plugin.&nbsp;
&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Sagar K S
Team PluginHive

